---
title: Maple-Mustard Chicken Breasts with Brussels Sprouts and Sweet Potato Coins
description: Chicken, mustard and maple are culinary best pals for good reason! This oh-so-Canadian combo of maple and mustard on juicy chicken won't let you down. The hearty veggies complement the sweet and zesty glaze perfectly!
